# FreightCore UI

## Overview

FreightCore UI is the internal operations dashboard for the LogiCore OMS platform. It enables warehouse operators, dispatch teams, and administrators to manage shipment lifecycles through a modern Angular-based interface.

## Features

- Dashboard
- Shipment List
- Create Shipment
- Shipment Details
- Warehouse Operations
- Dispatch Management
- Shipment Timeline

## Technology Stack

- Angular
- TypeScript
- CSS

## Backend Dependency

This application connects to the **LogiCore OMS** backend.

Related Repository: `logicore-oms`

## License

Demo project developed for learning and portfolio purposes.
